{"id":25536,"date":"2024-02-28T23:02:11","date_gmt":"2021-09-28T17:32:11","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=25536"},"modified":"2022-06-30T16:50:06","modified_gmt":"2022-06-30T11:20:06","slug":"purple-curtains-for-bedroom","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/purple-curtains-for-bedroom\/","title":{"rendered":"Majestic And Peaceful: Purple Curtains For The Bedroom"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Skim through our fantastic collection of purple curtains for the bedroom and make your best pick for the next makeover, one that will give your private haven the rich and winning vibe you have always wanted&nbsp;<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Curtains play a significant role in the bedroom by giving it a complete and more refined look. Besides the standard brown and cream curtains widely available in the market today, purple curtains are also becoming quite popular.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here\u2019s why purple <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/curtain-designs-for-bedroom\/\">curtains designs for the bedroom<\/a> are high in demand:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>They are visually appealing and seamlessly complement\/contrast with the existing wall colours.&nbsp;<\/li><li>They are versatile as you play around with different shades to achieve certain effects.&nbsp;<\/li><li>They are available in the form of lightweight voiles (~fine soft sheer fabric) and heavy curtains (~blackout curtains).&nbsp;<\/li><li>They can provide both warmth and coolness to the area as they are a mix of red and blue.&nbsp;<\/li><li>They provide stability of mind and improve your concentration and memory.&nbsp;<\/li><li>They help you heal faster and sleep better, as per Vastu.&nbsp;<\/li><li>They are associated with imagination, ambition, creativity and luxury.<\/li><li>They are a symbol of spirituality, passion, peace and wisdom.<\/li><li>They bring a unique and distinctive personality to the space.&nbsp;<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tips To Keep In Mind While Choosing Purple Curtains For The Bedroom\/Curtains For A Purple Bedroom&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Choose lighter shades of purple for your curtains so that they make your white\/cream\/light grey-walled bedroom look larger and give out cooler vibes\u2014for example, lavender, lilac and pale violet.<\/li><li>Use slightly darker shades of purple to lend a more dramatic and vibrant look to your white\/cream\/light grey-walled bedroom\u2014for example, thistle, dark violet, plum, amethyst and electric purple.&nbsp;<\/li><li>If your bedroom has standard-sized windows, you can go in for slightly short-length curtains. However, if the windows are large, you can go in for full-length curtains that touch the floor.&nbsp;<\/li><li>Ensure that your curtains are at least two times the width of your bedroom window so that they hang properly and give a fuller look when they are drawn.&nbsp;<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>We\u2019ve compiled a list of the most amazing shades of purple curtains for your bedroom for you to get inspired. Without further ado, let\u2019s begin.&nbsp;<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Amethyst Curtains For The Bedroom For An Airy Look<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>These amethyst curtains for the bedroom look pretty whimsical and airy. The short curtains allow ample sunlight into the bedroom and also provide you with some level of privacy. The curtains perfectly match the purple accent wall and blend well with the decor of the bedroom.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/28221801\/amethyst-purple-curtains-for-bedroom-for-an-airy-look.jpg\" alt=\"Amethyst purple curtains for bedroom for an airy look with antique wood furniture designs \" class=\"wp-image-25537\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/28221801\/amethyst-purple-curtains-for-bedroom-for-an-airy-look.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/28221801\/amethyst-purple-curtains-for-bedroom-for-an-airy-look-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/28221801\/amethyst-purple-curtains-for-bedroom-for-an-airy-look-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/28221801\/amethyst-purple-curtains-for-bedroom-for-an-airy-look-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Pair these purple curtains with antique wood furniture designs to introduce a perfect balance of tradition and modernity<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Want to know what kind of bedroom designs suits you\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/02170353\/what-kind-of-bedroom-designs-suits-you.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Black, Purple And White Curtains For The Bedroom To Introduce An Opulent Vibe<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>These black, purple and white patterned curtains lend a rich, deep and opulent vibe to the bedroom. The dark wallpaper makes a bold visual statement while the bed linen and rug soften the look and feel of this space. The fancy chandelier and the designer side table serves as the icing on the cake.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/28222039\/black-dark-purple-and-white-curtains-for-bedroom-to-introduce-an-opulent-vibe.jpg\" alt=\"Black and purple curtains for bedroom to introduce an opulent vibe\" class=\"wp-image-25538\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/28222039\/black-dark-purple-and-white-curtains-for-bedroom-to-