ta curtains for the bedroom make the white bedroom look more graceful and sophisticated. Introduce hints of the same colour in the form of a medium rug and some photo frames to bring some cohesiveness and unity in the bedroom\u2019s design aesthetics.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/28224227\/purple-curtains-for-bedroom-for-increased-gracefulness.jpg\" alt=\"Purple curtains for bedroom for increased gracefulness where ambient lights in the bedroom to set the right mood\" class=\"wp-image-25541\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/28224227\/purple-curtains-for-bedroom-for-increased-gracefulness.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/28224227\/purple-curtains-for-bedroom-for-increased-gracefulness-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/28224227\/purple-curtains-for-bedroom-for-increased-gracefulness-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/28224227\/purple-curtains-for-bedroom-for-increased-gracefulness-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Add a mix of task lights and ambient lights in the bedroom to set the right mood of the room as and when needed<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All in all, you need to choose the right purple shade for your curtains as it will give the finishing touch to your bedroom and tie all the design elements together.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Wondering what shade of purple curtains will look great in your bedroom? Don\u2019t overthink; just get in touch with <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">Design Cafe, <\/a>and we\u2019ll gladly sort that out for you.  <\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home int